#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_2
msgid ""
"☕ <strong>Quality Coffee &amp; Tea</strong> – Fuel for a productive day "
"ahead."
msgstr ""
"☕ <strong>Café de qualidade &amp; Chá</strong> – Combustível para um dia "
"produtivo pela frente."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_3
msgid ""
"✍ <strong>Hands-On Exercises</strong> – Apply new methods immediately to "
"your work."
msgstr ""
"✍ <strong>Exercícios práticos do</strong> – Aplique os novos métodos "
"imediatamente ao seu trabalho."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_1
msgid ""
"🍹 <strong>Drinks &amp; Snacks</strong> – A curated selection to keep the "
"conversation flowing."
msgstr ""
"🍹 <strong>Bebidas &amp; Petiscos</strong> – Uma seleção especial para "
"manter a conversa fluindo."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_2
msgid ""
"👋 <strong>Morning Networking</strong> – Meet fellow members before diving "
"into work."
msgstr ""
"👋 <strong>Networking matinal</strong> – Conheça outros membros antes de "
"mergulhar no trabalho."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_1
msgid ""
"💡 <strong>Inspiration</strong> – Exchange ideas in a relaxed, social "
"setting."
msgstr ""
"💡 <strong>Inspiração</strong> – Troque ideias em um ambiente descontraído e "
"social."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_3
msgid ""
"🤝 <strong>Collaborative Atmosphere</strong> – Connect with others who value "
"creativity and growth."
msgstr ""
"🤝 <strong>Ambiente colaborativo</strong> – Conecte-se com outras pessoas "
"que valorizam a criatividade e o crescimento."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_1
msgid ""
"🤝 <strong>Networking</strong> – Meet entrepreneurs, freelancers, and "
"creatives."
msgstr ""
"🤝 <strong>Networking</strong> – Conheça empreendedores, freelancers e "
"criativos."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_2
msgid ""
"🥯 <strong>Fresh Bagels</strong> – With a variety of toppings to suit every "
"taste."
msgstr ""
"🥯 <strong>Bagels frescos</strong> – Com uma variedade de coberturas para "
"todos os gostos."

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_3
msgid ""
"🧠 <strong>Proven Strategies</strong> – Learn practical tools to stay "
"productive and inspired."
msgstr ""
"🧠 <strong>Estratégias comprovadas</strong> – Aprenda ferramentas práticas "
"para se manter produtivo e inspirado."

